Multiplayer Snake Game:-

Using C++ graphics libraries 
------------------------
Compilation: g++ snake.cpp -lGLU -lGL -lglut

Instructions:

player 1(blue snake):
--------------------

       w          ---->forward
a             d   ---->sideways
       s          ---->backward


player 2(red snake):
--------------------
      u          ----->forward
h            k   ----->sideways
      j          ----->backward




